import {Switch, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import './Main.css'

const Main = () => (
    <main>
        <Switch>
            <Route path="/about">
                <About />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/users">
                <Users />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/">
                <Home />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
      </main>
);

export default Main;
